FEATURES


Shooter mechanics with different weapon

  • Pistol

  • Grenade gun
  • Firethrower
  • Shotgun
  • Machinegun
  • Grenades
  • Switch weapon
  • Ammo
  • 5 types of AI


Tanks

  • Gun
  • Machinegun
  • Smoke grenades
  • Different damage depending on the place of hit

Planes

  • Different weapon and character skins
